 ReasonML) at the very least. At a certain point, doesn't matter how well you organize, navigating and remembering actions becomes a huge pain."), mdx("p", null, "It speaks volume, when the creator of Redux, Dan Abramov, expressed disappointment in what its tool came to be (or how people use it). Researching and getting to know Redux sparked a very interesting dilemma: manage an app' state entirely in global state and dumb down all your components; or use global state only for ", mdx("em", {
